<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Trusted Household Care Dubai | Vetted Nannies, Babysitters & Household Staff</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <meta name="description" content="Trusted Household Care helps Dubai families find vetted nannies, babysitters, housekeepers, and household staff through a private, consultation-led introduction process.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://trustedhouseholdcare.com/">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 id="hero-title">Vetted Nannies, Babysitters & Household Staff in Dubai</h1>
<p id="hero-sub">Trusted Household Care helps families in Dubai find vetted nannies, babysitters, housekeepers, maternity nurses, and household staff through a structured introduction process. Every candidate is reviewed before being introduced to families.</p>
<div class="hero-cta-row">
                <a href="/book" class="cta-btn" id="hero-cta">Request Staff</a>
                <a href="/candidates" class="cta-btn secondary hero-secondary">View Candidate Shortlist</a>
            </div>
            <ul class="hero-badges" aria-label="How we protect privacy">
                <li><span class="hero-badge-icon">&#128274;</span> Candidate privacy protected</li>
                <li><span class="hero-badge-icon">&#128196;</span> CVs after consultation</li>
                <li><span class="hero-badge-icon">&#9989;</span> References by request</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="services-preview">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#128118;</div>
                <h3 id="card1-title">Professional Nannies</h3>
                <p id="card1-desc">English-speaking specialists focusing on child development, safety, and cultural education.</p>
                <a href="/nanny-in-dubai" class="card-link">Nanny in Dubai &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#128155;</div>
                <h3>Trusted Babysitters</h3>
                <p>Flexible evening, weekend, and occasional childcare support introduced through a private process.</p>
                <a href="/babysitter-in-dubai" class="card-link">Babysitter in Dubai &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#127860;</div>
                <h3 id="card2-title">Private Chefs</h3>
                <p id="card2-desc">Expertise in Asian and International cuisines, managing household nutrition and events.</p>
                <a href="/services" class="card-link">Learn More &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#127968;</div>
                <h3 id="card3-title">Executive Housekeepers</h3>
                <p id="card3-desc">Meticulous home management and organization according to 5-star hospitality standards.</p>
                <a href="/housekeeper-in-dubai" class="card-link">Housekeeper in Dubai &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shortlist-section">
        <div class="shortlist-inner">
            <div class="shortlist-text">
                <h2>Private candidate shortlists</h2>
                <p>Preview the quality of our household and childcare professionals through an exclusive, private shortlist — personally reviewed and screened, with reference checks where available. To protect candidate privacy, direct contact details are never published; introductions are coordinated through Trusted Household &amp; Childcare after consultation.</p>
                <a href="/candidates" class="cta-btn">View the shortlist</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-trust">
        <h2 class="section-title">How trust works</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">A calm, structured process — so the right introductions reach your family without the noise of a public database.</p>
        <div class="how-trust-grid">
            <div class="how-step">
                <span class="how-step-num">1</span>
                <h3>We understand your household</h3>
                <p>We start with a consultation to learn how your home runs, what your family needs, and the qualities that matter most to you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-step">
                <span class="how-step-num">2</span>
                <h3>We review suitable candidates</h3>
                <p>Each profile is personally reviewed and screened, with reference checks where available, through a structured selection process.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-step">
                <span class="how-step-num">3</span>
                <h3>We share a private shortlist</h3>
                <p>You receive a small, considered shortlist matched to your household — never an open, searchable list of people.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-step">
                <span class="how-step-num">4</span>
                <h3>Introductions happen only through us</h3>
                <p>Direct contact details stay protected. We coordinate every introduction so the process feels safe for families and candidates alike.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-families">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why families trust us</h2>
        <div class="why-families-grid">
            <div class="why-family-item">
                <span class="why-family-icon">&#10003;</span>
                <h4>Personally reviewed profiles</h4>
                <p>Every candidate is reviewed and screened personally — not auto-listed from a database.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-family-item">
                <span class="why-family-icon">&#10003;</span>
                <h4>Candidate privacy protected</h4>
                <p>Direct contact details are never published. Privacy is protected on both sides of every introduction.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-family-item">
                <span class="why-family-icon">&#10003;</span>
                <h4>References by request</h4>
                <p>Reference details are shared only after consultation, when an introduction is genuinely moving forward.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-family-item">
                <span class="why-family-icon">&#10003;</span>
                <h4>Led by 25 years of household experience</h4>
                <p>Our review process is guided by Diana Rose, with 25 years of hands-on household and childcare experience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-us">
        <div class="why-grid">
            <div class="why-text">
                <h2>Why Trusted Household &amp; Childcare?</h2>
                <div class="why-item">
                    <h4>Careful Selection</h4>
                    <p>Every candidate is personally reviewed through a structured selection process — screened, vetted, and reference-checked where available — before we make an introduction.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-item">
                    <h4>International Coverage</h4>
                    <p>Serving international families worldwide, with priority coverage across Armenia, Georgia, Hong Kong, Japan, Singapore, the UAE, and Saudi Arabia.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-item">
                    <h4>Ongoing Support</h4>
                    <p>Dedicated account managers for the first 90 days and continuous check-ins throughout the placement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="why-image"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/trust-lead') %>

    <section class="compliance">
        <div class="badge" id="badge-text">International Coverage</div>
        <h2 id="comp-title">Global Standards, Personal Service</h2>
        <p id="comp-desc">We can discuss family requirements, candidate suitability, and local process considerations during consultation. Operated by SUNRISE GLOBAL SOLUTIONS - FZCO.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Find Your Perfect Household Professional?</h2>
        <p>Schedule a complimentary consultation with our placement specialists.</p>
        <a href="/book" class="cta-btn">Get Started</a>
    </section>
</section>

<section id="faq" class="faq-section" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
    <div class="faq-inner">
        <div class="faq-heading">
            <span class="faq-kicker">Family guidance</span>
            <h2 id="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Clear answers for families considering private household and childcare introductions in Dubai.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
            <details class="faq-item" open>
                <summary>
                    <span>How do I hire a nanny in Dubai?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Trusted Household Care helps families in Dubai identify suitable nannies through a calm, structured introduction process. Each candidate is reviewed before being introduced to your family.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>What is the difference between a nanny and a babysitter?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>A nanny usually provides ongoing childcare support and becomes part of a family&rsquo;s regular routine, while a babysitter is typically engaged for occasional or short-term childcare needs.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>Do you provide housekeepers in Dubai?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes. Families can request introductions to experienced housekeepers, household assistants, and other domestic staff depending on their household requirements.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>How are candidates screened?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Candidate profiles are reviewed through a structured selection process that may include interviews, experience verification, reference checks where available, and suitability assessment before introduction.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>Can I request a consultation before reviewing candidates?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes. We begin with a consultation to understand your household requirements, preferences, and expectations before recommending suitable candidates.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

